* Apache mods need to be enable
--------------
	- Expire
	- Rewrite
	- Deflate

* Some Package have to be installed via apt :
--------------

	+ PHP
	- php5
	- php-pear
	- php5-mysqli
	- php5-pgsql
	- php5-curl
	- php5-xmlrpc
	- php5-json

	+ Services
	- gettext
	- imagemagick
	- memcached
	- pwgen
	- java 1.6

	+ Css compression
	- csstidy

* Some Package have to be installed via pecl :
--------------

	+ PHP
	- apc
    - memcache

* Locales need to be available on system
--------------

# find . -type f -iname "*.php" | xgettext --keyword=__ -j -s -o message.pot -f -
# --msgid-bugs-address=ADRESSE@COURRIEL

	+ linux locale
	- bg_BG.UTF-8
	- de_DE.UTF-8
	- en_GB.UTF-8
	- en_US.UTF-8
	- es_ES.UTF-8
	- fr_FR.UTF-8
	- it_IT.UTF-8
	- ru_RU.UTF-8

* Init Project
-------------
Example:
$ find . -iname *.php | sed 's/ /\\ /g' | sed 's/#/\#/g' | xargs sed -i 's#MyProject#NewProject#gi'

